<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14140063840606885972">Mike Davis is a social commentator, urban theorist, historian, and political activist. He is best known for his investigations of power and social class in his native Southern California. He is the recipient of the MacArthur Fellowship and the Lannan Literary Award. He lives in San Diego.</span>

